data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story home nestled in this nice Terrell neighborhood. As you approach, you'll be greeted by a welcoming front porch that invites you to sit back, relax, and enjoy the view. The elegant bay windows on the front of the house not only enhance its curb appeal but also flood the interior with natural light. Stepping inside, you'll find a thoughtfully designed layout that combines modern convenience with classic charm. Upstairs, you'll discover spacious bedrooms offering serene views of the surrounding area. This home features a generously sized backyard, providing plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation. This is a perfect place to create lasting memories! Whether you're sipping your morning coffee on the front porch or hosting a barbecue in the backyard, this home is designed to make every day feel like a special occasion. Information provided is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed and should be verified by buyer and buyer's agent.
